1
00:00:02,620 --> 00:00:07,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's been one week since 
Ishino the Musician died.</i></font>

2
00:00:10,880 --> 00:00:13,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>To find out who was responsible,</i></font>

3
00:00:13,100 --> 00:00:17,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>we raided the lair of a Dark Lord,
the Count of Twin Pincers,</i></font>

4
00:00:17,920 --> 00:00:20,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but all we got our hands
on were underlings.</i></font>

5
00:00:23,040 --> 00:00:25,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And with not much intel to show for it.</i></font>

6
00:00:32,520 --> 00:00:36,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It looks like I'm gonna need to 
get a little more creative.</i></font>

7
00:00:41,310 --> 00:00:45,020
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#4c413a"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="40">Scum of the Brave</font></b></font></font></font>

8
00:02:17,860 --> 00:02:19,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Another bouquet of flowers.</font>

9
00:02:18,450 --> 00:02:22,870
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#010000"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>A Brave's Legacy</b></font></font></font>

10
00:02:19,690 --> 00:02:22,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Make them stop sending them here.</font>

11
00:02:30,750 --> 00:02:33,770
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="12"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#666159">Dear "Reaper" Yashiro</font></font></font></font>

12
00:02:30,750 --> 00:02:33,770
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="12"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#666159">This season is marked by clear skies and stars that dazzle more beautifully than the rest of the year.</font></font></font></font>

13
00:02:30,750 --> 00:02:33,770
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="12"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#666159">To that end, I would like to invite you to a small affair 
in which we will take full enjoyment of these long winter nights.</font></font></font></font>

14
00:02:30,750 --> 00:02:33,770
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="12"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#666159">Vintage wine of the finest grade will be served as we discuss our various goals,
 which I hope will make for a sublime evening.</font></font></font></font>

15
00:02:31,760 --> 00:02:33,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, this works.</font>

16
00:02:34,230 --> 00:02:37,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A literal invitation. What a joke.</font>

17
00:02:39,510 --> 00:02:41,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good day! It's me!</font>

18
00:02:41,590 --> 00:02:44,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master! Why did you ignore the—</font>

19
00:02:45,550 --> 00:02:47,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is that bouquet?!</font>

20
00:02:47,640 --> 00:02:49,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it for you?</font>

21
00:02:49,410 --> 00:02:51,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nope. For Ed.</font>

22
00:02:52,800 --> 00:02:55,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I had no idea he was so popular!</font>

23
00:02:55,880 --> 00:02:57,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">More importantly, Master!</font>

24
00:02:57,280 --> 00:03:02,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why didn't you come to observe 
the practical exam last week?!</font>

25
00:03:04,150 --> 00:03:05,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right.</font>

26
00:03:05,740 --> 00:03:08,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I never intended to.</font>

27
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:11,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where's the other one? Sara.</font>

28
00:03:11,820 --> 00:03:14,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She has cleanup duty at school!</font>

29
00:03:19,130 --> 00:03:22,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The daughter of King Arthur 
cleaning the school grounds...</font>

30
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:25,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, did you two pass that exam?</font>

31
00:03:26,230 --> 00:03:28,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sara and I did.</font>

32
00:03:28,480 --> 00:03:30,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aki got a draw and has 
to take a makeup exam.</font>

33
00:03:30,550 --> 00:03:36,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes! My opponent, Sakakibara 
Helen, was a fearsome foe!</font>

34
00:03:41,130 --> 00:03:44,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I struck, and she evaded, only for <i>her</i> 
to strike, forcing <i>me</i> to evade!</font>

35
00:03:44,130 --> 00:03:46,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was a close-fought battle!</font>

36
00:03:47,120 --> 00:03:50,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One could say it was a white-knuckled
battle of epic proportions!</font>

37
00:03:57,560 --> 00:03:58,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously?</font>

38
00:04:00,070 --> 00:04:03,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought the opponent
was pretty average.</font>

39
00:04:03,050 --> 00:04:05,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They were so evenly matched, 
it devolved into a drag.</font>

40
00:04:05,390 --> 00:04:10,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yukine! I would appreciate it if you 
embellished my exploits around Master!</font>

41
00:04:10,720 --> 00:04:13,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If Indo says they were average,</font>

42
00:04:13,300 --> 00:04:15,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">they must've been half decent.</font>

43
00:04:15,770 --> 00:04:17,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like my lessons had an effect.</font>

44
00:04:18,210 --> 00:04:21,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if the fight dragged on that long,</font>

45
00:04:21,590 --> 00:04:24,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you still haven't fixed 
what I warned you about.</font>

46
00:04:24,320 --> 00:04:27,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were passive, aimed for counters, 
and tried to win on points, right?</font>

47
00:04:28,540 --> 00:04:33,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes! But I like to think that I 
have taken your lessons to heart.</font>

48
00:04:33,280 --> 00:04:36,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The technique for disarming 
foes that you used...</font>

49
00:04:36,400 --> 00:04:39,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I believe it's called a
kote-uchi in kendo.</font>

50
00:04:40,700 --> 00:04:43,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I made good use of it.</font>

51
00:04:43,080 --> 00:04:46,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your nonlethal intentions... 
are something I have inherited.</font>

52
00:04:47,930 --> 00:04:52,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look, I only used it because killing 
them would've been a big headache.</font>

53
00:04:52,870 --> 00:04:55,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, now, there's no need
for such modesty!</font>

54
00:04:55,620 --> 00:04:56,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Listen to me, damn it!</font>

55
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:59,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You think I'm trying to not be lethal?</font>

56
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:03,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Next time you get a chance, 
get a good read on my mind.</font>

57
00:05:04,960 --> 00:05:07,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Read your mind, Master?!</font>

58
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:21,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No! I think we need to get to 
know each other better first!</font>

59
00:05:21,440 --> 00:05:23,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That sort of relationship...</font>

60
00:05:23,550 --> 00:05:24,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">would be inappropriate!</font>

61
00:05:25,890 --> 00:05:28,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Somehow that was an even more 
annoying reaction than I anticipated.</font>

62
00:05:28,970 --> 00:05:31,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Instructor. When's my next lesson?</font>

63
00:05:32,710 --> 00:05:34,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm kinda busy for the foreseeable future.</font>

64
00:05:34,950 --> 00:05:37,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you said you'd train me more.</font>

65
00:05:37,350 --> 00:05:38,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You promised.</font>

66
00:05:39,440 --> 00:05:41,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did I, now?</font>

67
00:05:41,860 --> 00:05:44,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You did. I know you did.</font>

68
00:05:45,500 --> 00:05:46,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fine, then.</font>

69
00:05:47,780 --> 00:05:50,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You girls busy this Saturday?</font>

70
00:05:52,570 --> 00:05:54,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No! We are in fact completely free!</font>

71
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:56,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What kind of lesson will this be?</font>

72
00:05:58,640 --> 00:06:00,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Social studies?</font>

73
00:06:02,540 --> 00:06:06,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, we'll meet up at 6PM in 
front of Ikebukuro Station.</font>

74
00:06:06,230 --> 00:06:08,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll notify Sara.</font>

75
00:06:08,720 --> 00:06:10,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't eat anything the day of.</font>

76
00:06:11,510 --> 00:06:15,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a good chance
you'll puke if you do.</font>

77
00:06:15,440 --> 00:06:18,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, that wasn't what surprised me...</font>

78
00:06:18,590 --> 00:06:20,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're going to contact Sara?</font>

79
00:06:20,440 --> 00:06:22,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How, exactly?</font>

80
00:06:22,030 --> 00:06:23,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, by text?</font>

81
00:06:24,080 --> 00:06:25,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Texting?!</font>

82
00:06:25,940 --> 00:06:30,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master! Why do you have
Sara's contact info?!</font>

83
00:06:30,120 --> 00:06:31,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because we exchanged them?</font>

84
00:06:31,780 --> 00:06:33,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">An exchange?!</font>

85
00:06:33,730 --> 00:06:37,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's so cruel! We haven't 
exchanged such information yet!</font>

86
00:06:37,450 --> 00:06:42,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I can't believe Sara had the gall to 
do so ahead of me, the first apprentice!</font>

87
00:06:40,790 --> 00:06:42,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Please, please shut up.</font>

88
00:06:42,350 --> 00:06:43,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Instructor.</font>

89
00:06:44,010 --> 00:06:45,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Unacceptable!</font>

90
00:06:44,010 --> 00:06:47,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me too. I want to exchange contact info.</font>

91
00:06:48,990 --> 00:06:51,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fine, but do you even have a phone?</font>

92
00:06:55,400 --> 00:06:56,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sometimes.</font>

93
00:06:56,830 --> 00:06:57,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sometimes...?</font>

94
00:06:58,060 --> 00:07:00,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master! Me as well!</font>

95
00:07:00,020 --> 00:07:02,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please, let us exchange
contact information!</font>

96
00:07:03,790 --> 00:07:05,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With <i>you</i>, Jogamine?!</font>

97
00:07:08,510 --> 00:07:14,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master, I feel there is an undeniable bias 
in the way you treat Yukine versus me...</font>

98
00:07:15,090 --> 00:07:16,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why wouldn't there be?</font>

99
00:07:33,110 --> 00:07:33,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There we go.</font>

100
00:07:34,160 --> 00:07:38,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you believe Ishino was sitting 
on top of all this gunpowder?</font>

101
00:07:38,680 --> 00:07:41,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hope you don't mind me hogging it all.</font>

102
00:07:41,690 --> 00:07:46,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine. I wouldn't know 
what to do with it, anyway.</font>

103
00:07:46,700 --> 00:07:49,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">More importantly, did you find it?</font>

104
00:07:49,670 --> 00:07:53,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. It was a real treasure trove.</font>

105
00:08:00,360 --> 00:08:03,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Joe! We're gonna play later,
 winner takes all!</font>

106
00:08:03,660 --> 00:08:06,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a Pantheon of Plagues 
you can have for free.</font>

107
00:08:06,620 --> 00:08:08,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Screw that card!</font>

108
00:08:08,620 --> 00:08:12,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">More importantly, what about Tidal 
Wave? He would always use that—</font>

109
00:08:11,590 --> 00:08:12,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Hey.</font>

110
00:08:14,060 --> 00:08:16,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I showed up because you said 
you needed a favor.</font>

111
00:08:16,670 --> 00:08:18,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is this?</font>

112
00:08:18,170 --> 00:08:20,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you two are just gonna play,
I'm heading out.</font>

113
00:08:20,930 --> 00:08:24,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My bad. Don't sulk so hard.</font>

114
00:08:24,030 --> 00:08:26,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not sulking!</font>

115
00:08:28,120 --> 00:08:30,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's something I need 
to confirm, actually.</font>

116
00:08:32,400 --> 00:08:34,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Remember your last lesson?</font>

117
00:08:34,840 --> 00:08:39,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those two we ran into aren't involved 
with the Round Table, are they?</font>

118
00:08:40,870 --> 00:08:43,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't think so.</font>

119
00:08:43,500 --> 00:08:46,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not like I know everybody, though.</font>

120
00:08:46,720 --> 00:08:48,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about your dad?</font>

121
00:08:48,420 --> 00:08:49,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He mention anything?</font>

122
00:08:51,300 --> 00:08:54,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't really like talking to him.</font>

123
00:08:54,190 --> 00:08:56,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can never tell what he's thinking.</font>

124
00:08:57,190 --> 00:09:02,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a good chance he knows what 
happened that night, though. I think.</font>

125
00:09:03,450 --> 00:09:04,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why's that?</font>

126
00:09:04,710 --> 00:09:06,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not sure.</font>

127
00:09:06,270 --> 00:09:09,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Might have something to do 
with his ether perception.</font>

128
00:09:10,160 --> 00:09:14,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">During the thing with the 
Count of Amber Thorns,</font>

129
00:09:14,880 --> 00:09:17,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">he knew you rescued me without 
me ever telling him, Sensei.</font>

130
00:09:20,380 --> 00:09:21,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That it?</font>

131
00:09:21,990 --> 00:09:24,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nope. My favor involves this stuff.</font>

132
00:09:26,240 --> 00:09:28,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a job only you can do.</font>

133
00:09:36,730 --> 00:09:39,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These are all women's clothes...</font>

134
00:09:39,090 --> 00:09:40,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are they yours?!</font>

135
00:09:40,630 --> 00:09:42,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hell no.</font>

136
00:09:42,960 --> 00:09:44,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was something Ishino was into.</font>

137
00:09:44,410 --> 00:09:45,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like what?!</font>

138
00:09:45,680 --> 00:09:47,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wouldn't ask, if I were you.</font>

139
00:09:48,720 --> 00:09:52,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need you to pick dresses fit 
for a party from this collection.</font>

140
00:09:52,130 --> 00:09:53,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll use them in the next lesson.</font>

141
00:09:53,770 --> 00:09:55,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For a party?</font>

142
00:09:55,580 --> 00:09:58,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I take it I'm picking out what I wear?</font>

143
00:09:58,370 --> 00:10:01,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. Choose something for 
Jogamine and Indo, too.</font>

144
00:10:02,700 --> 00:10:05,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't mind, but why me?</font>

145
00:10:06,160 --> 00:10:09,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You really think having those two 
pick their outfits would work out?</font>

146
00:10:08,510 --> 00:10:09,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}This is it!</font>

147
00:10:12,640 --> 00:10:14,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Should we be going through 
his stuff like this?</font>

148
00:10:15,480 --> 00:10:17,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This happens all the time with Braves.</font>

149
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:23,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, the Pincers raid
didn't turn anything up?</font>

150
00:10:25,820 --> 00:10:27,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Out of the people Malta grabbed,</font>

151
00:10:27,830 --> 00:10:30,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">one of them had some intel.</font>

152
00:10:30,560 --> 00:10:33,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Didn't know anything about
that woman, Levi.</font>

153
00:10:34,550 --> 00:10:39,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But the guy, Ido, was a Brave who 
raised hell in Kansai until last year.</font>

154
00:10:39,740 --> 00:10:41,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He worked as a mercenary for Dark Lords</font>

155
00:10:41,970 --> 00:10:44,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and stuck his nose into all 
kinds of conflicts.</font>

156
00:10:44,790 --> 00:10:49,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And he was famous for never 
working with the losing side.</font>

157
00:10:56,800 --> 00:10:59,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Might have to do with
his ether perception.</font>

158
00:10:59,160 --> 00:11:00,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seems likely.</font>

159
00:11:01,260 --> 00:11:04,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He acted like he knew how 
strong I was when he saw me.</font>

160
00:11:05,450 --> 00:11:08,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Both of them are washed up 
Braves who became outlaws.</font>

161
00:11:14,160 --> 00:11:18,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And they were wandering
inside the academy...</font>

162
00:11:18,410 --> 00:11:23,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. At first, I had them pegged as new 
muscle for the Coffin Count of Storms.</font>

163
00:11:24,390 --> 00:11:27,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He may be allied with the
man from yesterday.</font>

164
00:11:27,290 --> 00:11:29,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He was fairly capable, wasn't he?</font>

165
00:11:30,970 --> 00:11:33,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't think they knew who I was.</font>

166
00:11:34,280 --> 00:11:37,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then running into you was a coincidence?</font>

167
00:11:37,680 --> 00:11:38,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hard to say.</font>

168
00:11:39,400 --> 00:11:44,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But we'll have to ask someone who's 
more in-the-know than Pincers.</font>

169
00:11:44,000 --> 00:11:46,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And since they went to the 
trouble of inviting me...</font>

170
00:11:49,720 --> 00:11:51,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you're taking them along?</font>

171
00:11:52,270 --> 00:11:54,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sounds pretty complicated.</font>

172
00:11:54,610 --> 00:11:58,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Taking you and Malta along 
would be like declaring war.</font>

173
00:11:58,320 --> 00:11:59,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm just going to talk.</font>

174
00:12:00,870 --> 00:12:02,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Part of it has to do with
his last words...</font>

175
00:12:08,190 --> 00:12:13,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The recorder Ishino always 
had on him had some data.</i></font>

176
00:12:17,490 --> 00:12:23,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello, Yashiro? Things have taken 
a turn for the interesting.</font>

177
00:12:23,910 --> 00:12:28,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm a bit busy at the moment, 
so I'll make this brief.</font>

178
00:12:29,370 --> 00:12:35,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Keep your eyes on your
three little friends.</font>

179
00:12:39,470 --> 00:12:44,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I sincerely doubt he was worried 
about the kids with his dying breath.</i></font>

180
00:12:45,850 --> 00:12:47,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>King Arthur's daughter.</i></font>

181
00:12:49,150 --> 00:12:50,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My master's daughter.</i></font>

182
00:12:51,760 --> 00:12:55,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And a girl who's weirdly used to killing.</i></font>

183
00:12:55,750 --> 00:13:00,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There's gotta be something
connecting them to the Half Dragon.</i></font>

184
00:13:01,840 --> 00:13:04,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not a softie like Pincers.</font>

185
00:13:05,870 --> 00:13:08,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If they insist on buzzing around me,</font>

186
00:13:08,260 --> 00:13:09,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm gonna make use of them.</font>

187
00:13:14,980 --> 00:13:19,980
<font size="20">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#f1f1f1"><b><font size="28">Scum of the Brave</font></b></font></font></font>

188
00:14:19,590 --> 00:14:21,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey. You're early.</font>

189
00:14:21,510 --> 00:14:24,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not really. More like right on time.</font>

190
00:14:24,830 --> 00:14:27,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And why didn't you give us
more of a heads-up to come armed?</font>

191
00:14:27,830 --> 00:14:30,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know how hard it is to find 
something that matches a dress?</font>

192
00:14:33,250 --> 00:14:35,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Her tastes are more girly than I figured.</i></font>

193
00:14:37,490 --> 00:14:38,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

194
00:14:38,530 --> 00:14:39,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing.</font>

195
00:14:39,880 --> 00:14:42,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You seemed to have dressed 
up pretty decent, is all.</font>

196
00:14:44,800 --> 00:14:46,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Must be nice, being a rich girl.</font>

197
00:14:46,910 --> 00:14:48,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bet your maid helped you get all set up.</font>

198
00:14:48,820 --> 00:14:55,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, no! And getting <i>them</i> ready 
was a real ordeal! Seriously!</font>

199
00:14:57,360 --> 00:14:58,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's hard to move in this.</font>

200
00:15:00,240 --> 00:15:02,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Was there nothing shorter?</font>

201
00:15:02,580 --> 00:15:05,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or maybe something like
what you're wearing, Sara.</font>

202
00:15:06,850 --> 00:15:09,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is pretty hard to get 
around in, too, trust me.</font>

203
00:15:09,700 --> 00:15:10,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?</font>

204
00:15:10,720 --> 00:15:12,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really.</font>

205
00:15:12,370 --> 00:15:15,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Plus, I picked a white dress 
that I thought would suit you.</font>

206
00:15:16,630 --> 00:15:18,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You like white, right?</font>

207
00:15:19,830 --> 00:15:20,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I do!</font>

208
00:15:20,960 --> 00:15:25,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sara! How do you explain the 
design of <i>my</i> dress, then?!</font>

209
00:15:25,610 --> 00:15:28,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look at how exposed I am!</font>

210
00:15:28,610 --> 00:15:33,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For someone with my beauty to go around 
in such... scantily clad fashion!</font>

211
00:15:33,870 --> 00:15:36,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be scouted as a model!</font>

212
00:15:36,920 --> 00:15:37,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go.</font>

213
00:15:39,620 --> 00:15:42,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why did you think this
dress would suit me?!</font>

214
00:15:42,620 --> 00:15:44,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Explain yourself, Sara!</font>

215
00:15:44,630 --> 00:15:48,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, you ask why, but...</font>

216
00:15:48,630 --> 00:15:50,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what Sensei picked out.</font>

217
00:15:55,320 --> 00:15:57,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see! As to be expected of Master!</font>

218
00:15:57,700 --> 00:15:59,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He has an eye for quality!</font>

219
00:15:59,050 --> 00:16:03,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was in a sour mood before, 
but I feel great now!</font>

220
00:16:03,400 --> 00:16:08,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sara and Indo's restraining clothing
 will make for a better lesson.</font>

221
00:16:08,920 --> 00:16:10,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jogamine, you're kinda terrible,</font>

222
00:16:11,550 --> 00:16:13,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so no handicap for you.</font>

223
00:16:13,030 --> 00:16:14,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'd be asking too much.</font>

224
00:16:14,530 --> 00:16:17,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are we doing for the lesson?</font>

225
00:16:17,660 --> 00:16:21,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Last time you reacted to a surprise 
attack with one-on-one matchups...</font>

226
00:16:21,540 --> 00:16:24,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it was a little too 
straightforward and no fun, right?</font>

227
00:16:25,830 --> 00:16:28,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, we're not exactly doing 
this for "fun."</font>

228
00:16:29,240 --> 00:16:31,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This time, you'll fight 
against multiple opponents,</font>

229
00:16:31,440 --> 00:16:34,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and you know going in
that they're hostile.</font>

230
00:16:37,060 --> 00:16:39,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's gonna be really 
exciting and educational</font>

231
00:16:39,700 --> 00:16:43,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">because you'll get to try 
out all kinds of techniques.</font>

232
00:16:44,240 --> 00:16:48,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A certain Dark Lord is throwing 
a little party today.</font>

233
00:16:49,850 --> 00:16:51,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Coffin Count of Storms.</font>

234
00:16:51,780 --> 00:16:54,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Arguably the strongest Dark 
Overlord in western Tokyo.</font>

235
00:16:55,450 --> 00:17:00,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You all know the Count of Twin Pincers.
He basically runs errands for them.</font>

236
00:17:03,250 --> 00:17:05,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In other words,
this is gonna be real simple.</font>

237
00:17:09,060 --> 00:17:12,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're gonna make this a party to remember!</font>

238
00:17:13,020 --> 00:17:14,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, Master!</font>

239
00:17:17,020 --> 00:17:22,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Dark Lords throw these kinds of 
parties for the intimidation factor.</i></font>

240
00:17:22,260 --> 00:17:24,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They put on a front of glitz and glamour</i></font>

241
00:17:24,180 --> 00:17:27,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>to show how powerful they are, 
both internally and to the outside.</i></font>

242
00:17:27,570 --> 00:17:33,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm pretty sure the the Coffin Count 
of Storms will be there in person.</i></font>

243
00:17:34,320 --> 00:17:38,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ishino's death happened on their turf.</i></font>

244
00:17:38,870 --> 00:17:41,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There's no denying they know something.</i></font>

245
00:17:41,830 --> 00:17:43,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm hungry.</font>

246
00:17:43,410 --> 00:17:45,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's going to be food, right?</font>

247
00:17:45,800 --> 00:17:47,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's the last thing I'm worried about!</font>

248
00:17:47,710 --> 00:17:51,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And Sensei, if it was gonna be like this,
you could've said something sooner!</font>

249
00:17:53,590 --> 00:17:58,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, Sara! Since when have you 
referred to Master as Sensei?!</font>

250
00:17:58,640 --> 00:18:01,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I normally don't overlook
that kind of thing!</font>

251
00:18:01,600 --> 00:18:02,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut up!</font>

252
00:18:03,430 --> 00:18:04,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're going!</font>

253
00:18:04,310 --> 00:18:06,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master!</font>

254
00:18:15,060 --> 00:18:17,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's quite the lively venue, isn't it?</font>

255
00:18:17,590 --> 00:18:19,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Quit gawking.</font>

256
00:18:19,520 --> 00:18:21,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're gonna think you're some bumpkin.</font>

257
00:18:35,980 --> 00:18:37,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome to the party.</font>

258
00:18:37,380 --> 00:18:40,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">May I have your name?</font>

259
00:18:42,380 --> 00:18:44,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am Ed Cyrus.</font>

260
00:18:44,550 --> 00:18:49,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I am here in the name of the 
great martial supernova, King Rob!</font>

261
00:18:49,550 --> 00:18:54,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was sent to offer my lord's regards 
to the Coffin Count of Storms.</font>

262
00:18:56,140 --> 00:18:57,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One moment, please.</font>

263
00:19:00,240 --> 00:19:01,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master!</font>

264
00:19:02,550 --> 00:19:06,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That man in the suit over there 
seems... very blue, for some reason.</font>

265
00:19:06,850 --> 00:19:09,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is he a Dark Lord?</font>

266
00:19:10,500 --> 00:19:12,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you seriously need to ask?!</font>

267
00:19:13,250 --> 00:19:18,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see! Then our aim is to subjugate 
the various assembled Dark Lords?</font>

268
00:19:19,020 --> 00:19:21,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not at all, no.</font>

269
00:19:21,790 --> 00:19:23,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But since we're here,</font>

270
00:19:23,740 --> 00:19:27,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I may as well warn you about 
which Dark Lords to avoid.</font>

271
00:19:27,460 --> 00:19:29,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't stare too hard.</font>

272
00:19:29,520 --> 00:19:31,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They'll take it personally.</font>

273
00:19:31,520 --> 00:19:32,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right!</font>

274
00:19:32,800 --> 00:19:37,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That blue devil-looking guy is the 
Judging Count of Silver String.</font>

275
00:19:37,270 --> 00:19:41,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Part of the Three-String Alliance 
that rules northern Tokyo.</font>

276
00:19:41,220 --> 00:19:44,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks outgoing enough, but he's 
a real dour, antisocial type.</font>

277
00:19:45,440 --> 00:19:49,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Over by the stairs is the 
Count of the Warped Garden.</font>

278
00:19:49,700 --> 00:19:51,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">An awful piece of work,</font>

279
00:19:51,790 --> 00:19:54,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so if he talks to you, just ignore him.</font>

280
00:19:54,960 --> 00:19:58,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Counts of Mournful 
Pulsation and Mournful Spray.</font>

281
00:19:58,530 --> 00:20:01,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just avoid them. Period.</font>

282
00:20:01,880 --> 00:20:03,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What did I say about staring?!</font>

283
00:20:03,690 --> 00:20:07,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you knew these bigwigs 
were gonna be here,</font>

284
00:20:07,020 --> 00:20:09,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">why didn't you warn us?!</font>

285
00:20:09,020 --> 00:20:12,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Learning to improvise is 
part of the lesson.</font>

286
00:20:13,100 --> 00:20:20,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry, sir, but the name Ed 
Cyrus was not on the guest list.</font>

287
00:20:20,010 --> 00:20:25,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would it be all right if I checked 
your identification or invitation?</font>

288
00:20:25,670 --> 00:20:27,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure, one sec...</font>

289
00:20:28,290 --> 00:20:29,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How's this?</font>

290
00:20:30,290 --> 00:20:32,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't happen to have 
my insurance card, so...</font>

291
00:20:37,840 --> 00:20:40,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's on. Go ahead and use E3.</font>

292
00:20:54,350 --> 00:20:56,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't shoot! You might hit the guests!</font>

293
00:20:57,290 --> 00:20:59,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They won't use guns in here.</font>

294
00:21:00,830 --> 00:21:03,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, for the opening act.</font>

295
00:21:06,450 --> 00:21:09,780
