299
00:22:35,020 --> 00:22:50,040
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="26"><font color="#feffff"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>Next Time</b></font></font></font></font>

300
00:22:35,520 --> 00:22:38,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Do you know the saying
"lead with the edge"?</i></font>

301
00:22:38,010 --> 00:22:41,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It means you can swing, but you won't
cut shit without a blade.</i></font>

302
00:22:41,300 --> 00:22:43,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A lesson that seems actually applicable!</i></font>

303
00:22:43,040 --> 00:22:44,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You're getting
the hang of this, Master!</i></font>

304
00:22:44,920 --> 00:22:47,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Next time is Episode 10, 
"A Brave's Instruction".</i></font>

305
00:22:47,280 --> 00:22:50,010
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#010000"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="24"><b>A Brave's Instruction</b></font></font></font></font>

306
00:22:47,840 --> 00:22:50,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Go, go, Master!</i></font>

